MICHIGAN ELITE BRIGADE CHAMPIONSHIP HISTORY

The Michigan Elite Brigade is a proven training ground for Michigan's Top High School Players.

Michigan Amateur Hockey Association Split Season State Championship 2014 (U18)

Chelsea Summer Showcase Champions 2014 (U18)

Northern Lakes Prospects Invitational Champions 2014 (U18)

HISTORY ALL-STATE PLAYERS

The Michigan Elite Brigade is a proven training ground for Michigan's Top High School Players. Numerous Elite Brigade Team Members and Development Camp players have moved on to play in NCAA, ACHA, NAHL, NCDC, CCHL, OJHL, EHL, SJHL, NOJHL, WSHL, USPHL.
